    "title": "Lead Revenue Manager at Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Revenue Manager with drive and ambition, Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions in Meerut is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions:\nAnanda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions!",
